  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Orally Administered DS102 in Patients With Acute Alcoholic Hepatitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomised, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Phase II Study to Assess the Efficacy and Safety of Orally Administered DS102 in Patients With Acute Decompensated Alcoholic Hepatitis.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
