  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this randomised, double-blind, placebo-controlled, phase II study is to assess&#xD;
      the efficacy and safety of orally administered DS102 in patients with acute decompensated&#xD;
      alcoholic hepatitis&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
